General.Name: Shanghai HIUV New Materials Co Ltd
General.Description: Shanghai HIUV New Materials Co.,Ltd engages in the research and development, manufacture, and sale of polymer films in China. It provides white ethylene-vinyl acetate film and PVE color glass adhesive film. The company also offers technical support and solutions for customers in various fields. Shanghai HIUV New Materials Co.,Ltd was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Shanghai, China.
